          "rangeStart": 1044,
          "rangeEnd": 1101,
          "markText": "由甲子检公元，须有相近之年以为旁证而推知之；盖甲子六十年一转，相同者甚多也。若由公元检甲子，则不劳考证，一检即得。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1751549082,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-03 21:24:42",
          "chapterUid": 16,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24919526&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1044&rangeEnd=1101",
